e/Tokyo\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 1.4040420891902658e-14, \"text\": \"Tokyo\", \"types\": [\"Q515\", \"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tokyo\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tokyo\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Yulo looks to complete his unfinished Olympic business as he returns to action in the all-around final on Wednesday, July 31.\", \"from\": 2501, \"to\": 2626, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Meanwhile, the floor exercise and vault finals are scheduled on August 3 and 4, respectively.- Rappler.com  How does this make you feel?\", \"from\": 2628, \"to\": 2764, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"follow us\", \"from\": 2766, \"to\": 2775, \"entities\": []}]}"